Introduction

Kwon Chaewon, also known as Eunchae is a South Korean singer. She used to be a member of the now-disbanded girl group DIA and its sub-unit L.U.B.

On March 7, 2016, Eunchae was introduced as the newest member of DIA and eventually made her official debut on June 14, when the group released their mini album called "Happy Ending." Seven years later, following DIA's disbandment, Eunchae joined the survival show "Universe Ticket" using her real name Kwon Chaewon, but ended up being eliminated in the 5th episode.
